snippet.textDisplay: Loads of thanks to Ram Sampath, Sona, Rituraj and the entire team for taking Odia music to global. Sona's voice texture for this song is Supperb👍. Especially Rituraj is extraordinary in singing state anthem of Odisha "BANDE UTKALA JANANI". Must be a Goosebumps moment for every Odia.❤
